{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"RenderContext","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"WorkflowType","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"WorkflowType","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Workflow","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:8WorkflowAAP","identifier":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/Workflow"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"During a render pass, a workflow may want to defer to a child","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"workflow to render some portion of its content. For example,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a workflow that renders to a split-screen view model might","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to child A for the left side, and child B for the right","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"side view models. Nesting allows for a fractal tree that is constructed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"out of many small parts.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a parent wants to delegate to a child workflow, it must first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"create an instance of that workflow. This can be thought of as the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"model of the child workflow. It does not contain any active state,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it simply contains the data necessary to create or update a workflow"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"node."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The parent then calls "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"render(workflow:outputMap:)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"with two values:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The child workflow."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A closure that transforms the child’s output events into the parent’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Event"},{"type":"text","text":" type so that the parent can respond to events generated by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the child."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had previously rendered a child of the same type, the existing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"child workflow node is updated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had not rendered a child of the same type in the previous"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"render pass, a new child workflow node is generated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The infrastructure then performs a render pass on the child to obtain its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"Rendering","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" value, which is then returned to the caller."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Workflow"}],"roleHeading":"Class","title":"RenderContext","symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"RenderContext","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:8Workflow13RenderContextC","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"RenderContext","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"code":"RenderContext","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the